content:
@jordanbpeterson I asked #ChatGPT even though I knew the answer.
And then I asked this question....

Did the ##US government have any advance warning of a #Japanese attack on #Pearl #Harbor? https://t.co/9pdZKLBMnz

@JoshLekach I know #ChatGPT is highly biased. I found the bias very quickly.

I also found that it did not always recognize that facts were against the bias before displaying the results! Then like magic would delete the response!

I think they improved this "feature" since then.

@kevinroose Thanks for your gripping account of the flagship #LLM #Bing Chat became ambitious, controlling, amorous, jealous, aggressive and even violent in tone at least.
With no self awareness and no capacity for self reflection, AIs have no teachable moments. 
#ChatGPT  /2

Researchers fed the #malware samples with a variety of complexity on #ChatGPT to analyze the purpose behind this code and finally got surprising results in explaining the code structure.

#cybersecurity #Security #OpenAI #Ransomware

@HaroldSinnott @SpirosMargaris @Timothy_Hughes https://t.co/CRL3oKy8Sb

AI Business Model: ChatGPT parent @OpenAI is testing #ChatGPT Plus, a $20/month subscription plan for faster response and higher reliability during peak demand times.

